      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "COUNTRY BOYS: Tribute to Alan Jackson, Garth Brooks, Brad Paisley & George Strait"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>COUNTRY BOYS</b> - A high-energy tribute to the music of Alan Jackson, Garth Brooks, Brad Paisley, and George Strait.</p>\n\n<p>Picture all four country legends sharing one stage for one unforgettable night. The <b>COUNTRY BOYS TRIBUTE SHOW</b> brings that experience to life with an electrifying live show that captures the sound, spirit, and energy of these iconic artists.</p>\n\n<p>Starring Scott Delhunty, Gerald Delhunty, Marc Babin, and Daniel Goguen—alongside five top-notch musicians—the band performs many of the timeless hits you know and love, including <i>Chattahoochee</i>, <i>Friends in Low Places</i>, <i>The Fireman</i>, and <i>Mud on the Tires</i>.</p>\n\n<p> Some band-members of the Country Boys have shared the stage with country greats such as Toby Keith, Sammy Kershaw, Ken Mellons, and John Conlee.</p>\n\n<p>If you're a true country music fan, this is one show you won't want to miss!</p>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
