      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Over the years, Sampson has earned multiple awards and industry recognition for his songwriting, becoming a quiet constant in Canada's East Coast music scene. Dave will hit the legendary Bearly's stage with his fiery band for a one night only special performance.</p>\n\n<p style='color:red'><b>All sales are final - no refunds.</b><p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>\n"
