      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Truro Jr. A Bearcats - ROUND 3: GAME 5 | Edmundston Blizzard"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>ROUND THREE IS HERE!<br>\nDon't miss the Truro Junior 'A' Bearcats  as they take on Edmundston for the Metalfab MHL Cup 🏆</p>\n\n<p>The Bearcats have home ice advantage for Games 1 & 2, don't miss:<br>\n📅Game 1: Monday, April 20 @ 7PM<br>\n📅 Game 2: Tuesday, April 21 @ 7PM<br>\n\n<p>Last time the Bearcats were in the finals was 2022...now they're BACK. You've watched them work all season to get here. NOW it's time to show up and get LOUD. Let's pack the rink. Bring the energy & finish this!</p>\n\n<p><i>* Students / Military must provide ID <br>\n* Youth 12 years and under must be accompanied & supervised by an adult / guardian 16 years or older <br>\n* Children 5 and under are free, they do not require a ticket<br>\n* Family Four Pack is 2 adults and 2 students/youths - no exceptions/substitutions<br> \n* Season Pass is ONE Ticket for the entire season as Assigned Seating. Individual Game Ticket is GA<br>\n* Tickets have no cash / exchange value<br>\n* Tickets are non-refundable (in the event of rescheduled games, original tickets may be used to attend the new date)<br>\n* No Re-Entry <br>\n* Airhorns are prohibited<br>\n* Subject to Bag Searches Upon Entry</i></p>\n\n"
      }
    ],
